    <body>
      <section eId="sec_3310">
        <num>3310</num>
        <heading>Licenses for manufacture or distribution of controlled substances</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_3310__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the name and address of the licensee;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_3310__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the nature of the controlled substances, either by name or\nschedule, or both, which may be manufactured or distributed;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_3310__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>whether manufacture or distribution or both such activities are\npermitted by the license.\n  5. Upon application of a licensee, a license may be amended to allow\nthe licensee to relocate within the state or to add a manufacturing or\ndistributing activity or to add further substances or schedules to the\nmanufacturing or distribution activity permitted thereunder. The fee for\nsuch amendment shall be two hundred fifty dollars.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
